rid lg:grid-cols-[1fr,1.1fr] gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-center"><div class="space-y-3"><h3 class="text-[19px] font-normal text-foreground tracking-[-0.02em] leading-snug">Join our newsletter and stay up to date with everything AI</h3><p class="text-[13px] text-muted-foreground/60 max-w-md leading-[1.6]">There&#x27;s too much noise in AI, let&#x27;s filter it for you. Get a curated digest of models, benchmarks, and the analysis that matters, right in your inbox once a week.</p></div><div class="lg:justify-self-end w-full lg:max-w-md"><form><div class="hidden"></div><div class="flex gap-2 p-1.5 rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-white/[0.03] border border-black/[0.06] dark:border-white/[0.08] shadow-[0_1px_2px_rgba(0,0,0,0.04),0_4px_12px_rgba(0,0,0,0.02)] dark:shadow-[0_1px_2px_rgba(0,0,0,0.2),0_4px_12px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] transition-shadow duration-200 focus-within:shadow-[0_1px_2px_rgba(0,0,0,0.06),0_4px_16px_rgba(0,0,0,0.05)] dark:focus-within:shadow-[0_1px_2px_rgba(0,0,0,0.3),0_4px_16px_rgba(0,0,0,0.15)]"><input type="email" placeholder="you@example.com" required="" autoComplete="email" class="flex-1 h-9 rounded-lg px-3 text-sm bg-transparent text-foreground placeholder:text-muted-foreground/35 border-0 focus:outline-none transition-colors duration-150 disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed" value=""/><button type="submit" disabled="" class="h-9 px-4 rounded-lg group relative overflow-hidden text-[13px] font-medium bg-foreground text-background shadow-[0_1px_2px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1),inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.1)] dark:shadow-[0_1px_2px_rgba(0,0,0,0.3),inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.05)] hover:shadow-[0_2px_4px_rgba(0,0,0,0.15),inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.1)] dark:hover:shadow-[0_2px_4px_rgba(0,0,0,0.4),inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.05)] active:scale-[0.98] active:shadow-[0_0px_1px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] transition-all duration-150 ease-out disabled:opacity-40 disabled:cursor-not-allowed disabled:active:scale-100 disabled:shadow-none focus:outline-none focus-visib